@startuml IMS-DC-SDK End-to-End Flow

title 5G New Calling Terminal SDK (IMS Data Channel SDK) - End-to-End Flow

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam wrapWidth 200
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

' Define actors
actor "User" as User
actor "Remote Party" as Remote

' Define components by layer
package "Android Framework Layer" {
    component [Telecom Framework] as Telecom
    component [InCallService] as InCall
}

package "SDK Core Layer" {
    component [InCallServiceImpl] as InCallImpl

    package "Core Managers" {
        component [NewCallsManager] as CallMgr
        component [DCManager] as DCMgr
        component [MiniAppManager] as AppMgr
        component [ExpandingCapacityManager] as ECMgr
    }
}

package "Mini App Layer" {
    component [MiniAppActivity\n(WebView Container)] as WebView
    component [DSBridge\n(JS-Native Bridge)] as DSBridge
    component [Mini App\n(HTML5/Vue.js)] as MiniApp

    package "JavaScript API System" {
        component [JSApi] as JSApi
        component [JsEventDispatcherFactory] as Factory

        package "Event Dispatchers" {
            component [DCJsEventDispatcher] as DCDispatcher
            component [MiniAppJsEventDispatcher] as AppDispatcher
            component [FileJsEventDispatcher] as FileDispatcher
            component [ECJsEventDispatcher] as ECDispatcher
        }

        package "Use Cases" {
            component [DCMiniUseCase] as DCUseCase
            component [MiniAppMiniUseCase] as AppUseCase
            component [FileMiniUseCase] as FileUseCase
        }
    }
}

package "Terminal Interface Layer (AIDL)" {
    component [DCServiceManager] as DCService

    interface "IImsDataChannel" as IDC
    interface "IImsDataChannelCallback" as IDCCallback
    interface "IExpandingCapacity" as IEC
}

package "Modem/Chipset Layer" {
    component [5G Modem\n(IMS Data Channel\nImplementation)] as Modem
}

package "Network Layer" {
    cloud "5G Network\n(IMS Core)" as Network
}

' Define relationships - Call Lifecycle Flow
User --> Telecom : Initiates/Receives Call
Telecom --> InCall : onBind()
InCall --> InCallImpl : Service Binding

InCallImpl --> CallMgr : Initialize (First Call)
InCallImpl --> DCMgr : Initialize (First Call)
InCallImpl --> AppMgr : Initialize (First Call)
InCallImpl --> ECMgr : Initialize (First Call)

CallMgr --> InCallImpl : onCallAdded Event
InCallImpl --> AppMgr : Notify Call Added

' Mini App Loading Flow
AppMgr --> WebView : Start Mini App
WebView --> MiniApp : Load HTML/JS
MiniApp --> DSBridge : Initialize Bridge
DSBridge --> JSApi : Register APIs

' Data Channel Creation Flow
User --> MiniApp : Click "Create DC"
MiniApp --> DSBridge : dsbridge.call('async', {...})
DSBridge --> JSApi : async(msg, handler)
JSApi --> Factory : getEventDispatcher('dc')
Factory --> DCDispatcher : Route Event
DCDispatcher --> DCUseCase : createAppDataChannel()
DCUseCase --> AppMgr : Validate & Process
AppMgr --> DCMgr : createDC(labels, description)
DCMgr --> DCService : createImsDc(labels, ...)
DCService --> IDC : AIDL Call
IDC --> Modem : Create Data Channels
Modem --> Network : Negotiate DC Creation
Network --> Remote : DC Negotiation

' Data Channel Response Flow
Network --> Modem : DC Created Response
Modem --> IDCCallback : onApplicationDataChannelResponse(dc)
IDCCallback --> DCMgr : Cache DC & Route
DCMgr --> AppMgr : onDataChannelCreated()
AppMgr --> MiniApp : Notify DC Ready
MiniApp --> User : Display "DC Created"

' Data Transmission Flow
MiniApp --> DSBridge : sendData(dcId, data)
DSBridge --> JSApi : async('dc', 'sendData', ...)
JSApi --> DCDispatcher : Route Event
DCDispatcher --> DCUseCase : sendData()
DCUseCase --> DCMgr : Get DC from Cache
DCMgr --> IDC : dc.send(data)
IDC --> Modem : Transmit Data
Modem --> Network : Send via IMS DC
Network --> Remote : Deliver Data

' Extended Capabilities Flow
MiniApp --> DSBridge : Call EC API (AI, Translation)
DSBridge --> JSApi : async('ec', ...)
JSApi --> ECDispatcher : Route Event
ECDispatcher --> ECMgr : Process Request
ECMgr --> IEC : Call OEM/Operator EC
IEC --> ECMgr : EC Response
ECMgr --> MiniApp : Return Result

' Call End Flow
User --> Telecom : End Call
Telecom --> InCallImpl : onCallRemoved()
InCallImpl --> AppMgr : Cleanup Mini Apps
InCallImpl --> DCMgr : Close All DCs
DCMgr --> IDC : close()
InCallImpl --> ECMgr : Release Resources

note right of InCallImpl
  Entry point of SDK
  - Monitors call lifecycle
  - Initializes all managers
  - Tied to active calls
end note

note right of DCMgr
  Data Channel Management
  - Queue-based DC creation
  - DC caching & reuse
  - State monitoring
  - Listener routing
end note

note right of AppMgr
  Mini App Lifecycle
  - App package management
  - Active/Passive startup
  - Auto-load policies
  - Multi-process support
  (up to 10 concurrent apps)
end note

note right of Factory
  Event Routing System
  - 'dc' → Data Channel ops
  - 'miniapp' → App control
  - 'file' → File operations
  - 'screen' → Screen sharing
  - 'ec' → Extended capabilities
  - 'system' → System info
end note

note bottom of Modem
  3GPP TS.71 Specification
  - IMS Data Channel
  - WebRTC-based (TS.66)
  - 5G New Calling
end note

@enduml
